            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What is your cancellation policy?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "Subscriptions can be cancelled at any time. If you choose to cancel after your order has been processed, you will still receive and be charged for that Boka order. Learn more at https://www.boka.com/policies/refund-policy"
